&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;ABOUT ROCKET MONEY 🔮&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Rocket Money’s mission is to empower people to live their best financial lives. Rocket Money offers members a unique understanding of their finances and a suite of valuable services that save them time and money – ultimately giving them a leg up on their financial journey.&lt;/p&gt;
